OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,FBy Maria Hassan
OL,9,FAn inclusive music movement developed
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland is making live
OL,11,Fperformance and composition accessible
OL,12,Fto everyone.
OL,14,FConductology - a gesture based system
OL,15,Fco-designed by researchers at Ulster
OL,16,FUniversity and disabled musicians - is
OL,17,Fnurturing the creative talents of
OL,18,Fyoung people with special needs,
OL,19,Fdeveloping new skills and building
OL,20,Fconfidence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,FThe system was devised by Dr Denise
OL,8,FWhite, who was inspired by her uncle
OL,9,FDesy who had Down Syndome and their
OL,10,Fshared love of music.
OL,12,FThe live composing sign language
OL,13,Fenables musicians with additional
OL,14,Fneeds to take part in collaborative
OL,15,Fmusic-making, equal to their
OL,16,Fmainstream peers.
OL,18,FDenise explained: "The system is 18
OL,19,Fgestures. We don't really plan it,
OL,20,Fit's semi-structured.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,F"The beauty about it is that the
OL,8,Fparticipants in front of you, they're
OL,9,Fjust totally engrossed in the actual
OL,10,Fcreating of the soundscape.
OL,12,F"Often it's token gestures, you know,
OL,13,Fa person with additional needs being
OL,14,Fhanded something and being told when
OL,15,Fto play, how to play.
OL,17,F"This system allows them to really
OL,18,Freach their creative potential and
OL,19,Fcreate fabulous music."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,FConductology is about more than
OL,8,Fcreative expression, participants are
OL,9,Flearning about themselves and
OL,10,Feducating others along the way.
OL,12,FMaster Conductologist Shaun Toye co-
OL,13,Fdesigned the system with Dr Denise.
OL,15,FHe told UTV: It has given me so much
OL,16,Fpassion, and so much growth and made
OL,17,Fme into a confident, strong man and
OL,18,Fhelped me find the key to the to my
OL,19,Fmusical journey."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,FPreparations are underway for an album
OL,8,Frelease and concert here at home, but
OL,9,Fthe vision is global.
OL,11,FThe Conductology network is expanding
OL,12,Fto nurseries, schools, and care
OL,13,Fsettings worldwide.
OL,15,FThe system is certainly hitting the
OL,16,Fright note at Rossmar School in
OL,17,FLimavady.
OL,19,F"Just waiting to hear what each pupil
OL,20,Fhas come up with themselves, what
OL,21,Fthey've composed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,F"Especially when we have our gestures
OL,8,Fwhere pupils are kind of playing with
OL,9,Feach other as opposed to in an entire
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,F"You can see the communication there,
OL,13,Fthey're sort of looking at me, looking
OL,14,Fat each other, they absolutely love
OL,15,Fit," teacher Erin Melville said.
OL,17,FIt's as much about the process as the
OL,18,Ffinal product, building confidence and
OL,19,Fenhancing social skills.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
