CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775772667
OL,3,CNI music movement 'realising the
OL,4,Ccreative potential' of young musicians
OL,5,Cwith SEN
OL,7,FMusician Sarah said: "Just seeing how
OL,8,Feveryone grows by playing music, how
OL,9,Feveryone has their wee moment, it's
OL,10,Ffantastic to see that everybody's
OL,11,Fhaving a chance to play what they like.
OL,13,F"It's just honestly unreal, seeing
OL,14,Feverybody grow and be proud of
OL,15,Fthemselves."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
